Valbona Yzeiraj was arrested on Thursday and pleaded not guilty to charges of assault, unauthorized practice of a profession and reckless endangerment . 
  Authorities said she illegally posed as dentist 'Dr Val' and pulled patients' teeth at a practice in Riverdale, New York . 
  She was fired from Ultimate Dental Care of Riverdale after the company found out she was illegally performing as a dentist . 
  The 45-year-old did injections in people's mouths and performed root canals . 
  She claimed to have dental training in Albania but had no license in the US . 
 